## Review Decision Matrix

| Category | Pass | Modify | Block |
|----------|------|--------|-------|
| Deployment strategy | Appropriate, reversible | Minor gaps | No rollback path |
| Health checks | Comprehensive, correct | Partial | Missing readiness |
| Rollback triggers | Defined, tested | Gaps | No auto-rollback for critical |
| Circuit breakers | Configured, fallbacks | Partial | No circuit breakers |
| Checklist | Complete, actionable | Incomplete | No checklist |
| Data migration | Safe, reversible | Gaps | Destructive, no rollback |

